Already before the second World War, fascinated Polish worked on spatial flights; they met not always comprehension.
I would want to evoke for example the lecture of A. Šternfeld to the astronomical observatory of Warsaw, December 6 1933, during which it presented pulled ideas of his work before keeps entitled "Introduction to astronautics".
